    "description_long": "This motorcycle features a classic design with a red fuel tank and side panels, contrasted by a black seat and frame. The front and rear fenders are painted in a light gray, and the wheels are spoked with black rims. The handlebars are upright and equipped with round mirrors and orange turn signals. The exhaust pipe is long and metallic, running along the right side of the bike. The overall build suggests a utilitarian, vintage style suitable for urban commuting.",
